<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-50 via-white to-blue-50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl" data-controller="exercise-checker">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col-reverse sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-2 sm:gap-4">
        <div class="bg-cyan-500 text-white text-md sm:text-xl px-2 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 rounded-lg font-bold">
          MORFOLOGIA
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-cyan-600">Preposizioni, congiunzioni, avverbi</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-cyan-600 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg sm:text-xl">
        179
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Esercizio 1: Sottolinea avverbi e aggettivi -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="word-highlighter">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-yellow-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">1</span>
      <span class="bg-yellow-400 text-blue-800 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm md:text-base font-bold mr-2">IMPARARE TUTTI</span>
      Sottolinea le parole evidenziate una volta se sono <strong class="underline text-blue-600">avverbi</strong>, due volte se sono <strong class="underline text-red-600">aggettivi</strong>.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Stai correndo <strong>troppo</strong>. (avverbio)</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Hai messo <strong>troppo</strong> sale nella pasta. (aggettivo)</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Il bagliore <strong>chiaro</strong> della luna illuminava la strada. (aggettivo)</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Non ci vedo <strong>chiaro</strong> in questa faccenda. (avverbio)</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Ci vuole <strong>molto</strong> coraggio. (aggettivo)</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Abbiamo riso <strong>molto</strong> allo spettacolo. (avverbio)</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Ho dormito <strong>parecchio</strong> e mi sono riposato. (avverbio)</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Ha speso <strong>parecchi</strong> soldi. (aggettivo)</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Esercizio 2: Completa con congiunzioni -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-blue-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">2</span>
      Completa le frasi con la <strong class="underline text-blue-600">congiunzione</strong> adatta.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Era ormai tardi</span>
        <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-400 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-600 w-24" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="perciò" placeholder="">
        <span class="text-gray-700">decisi di tornare a casa.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Mi sono bagnata</span>
        <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-400 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-600 w-24" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="perché" placeholder="">
        <span class="text-gray-700">non avevo portato l'ombrello.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3">
        <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-400 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-600 w-24" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="Se" placeholder="">
        <span class="text-gray-700">non hai capito, chiedi alla maestra</span>
        <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-400 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-600 w-24" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="affinché" placeholder="">
        <span class="text-gray-700">te lo spieghi di nuovo.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Il bus andava abbastanza veloce</span>
        <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-400 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-600 w-24" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="benché" placeholder="">
        <span class="text-gray-700">ci fosse molta nebbia.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Esercizio 3: Sottolinea avverbi che fungono da preposizioni -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-green-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="word-highlighter">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">3</span>
      Sottolinea in rosso gli <strong class="underline text-blue-600">avverbi</strong> che funzionano come <strong class="underline text-red-600">preposizioni</strong>.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="px-1 rounded cursor-pointer">Dopo</span> cena abbiamo assistito a un concerto.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Verrai <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="px-1 rounded cursor-pointer">da</span> me <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="px-1 rounded cursor-pointer">prima</span> della partenza?</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• La zia arriverà <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="px-1 rounded cursor-pointer">da</span> Roma <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="px-1 rounded cursor-pointer">dopo</span> le feste.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Ho trovato dei soldi <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="px-1 rounded cursor-pointer">sotto</span> l'armadio.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Il cellulare è <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="px-1 rounded cursor-pointer">sopra</span> il tavolo.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• La pasticceria è <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="px-1 rounded cursor-pointer">accanto</span> al ristorante.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Esercizio 4: Individua avverbi e locuzioni avverbiali -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-purple-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">4</span>
      Sottolinea in rosso gli <strong class="underline text-blue-600">avverbi</strong>, in blu le <strong class="underline text-red-600">locuzioni avverbiali</strong>. Poi scegli un avverbio e una locuzione avverbiale tra quelli che hai trovato e scrivi una frase per ciascuno.
    </h2>

    <div class="mb-4 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700">
      <p>Luca e Miriam abitano vicino e giocano spesso insieme. Di solito si incontrano nel pomeriggio al campetto da calcio. Si divertono molto a calciare il pallone in rete. Da qualche tempo si uniscono a loro anche altri bambini. Forse riusciranno a formare una vera e propria squadra.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">Avverbio:</span>
        <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-purple-400 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-purple-600 w-full" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="libera" placeholder="">
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">Locuzione avverbiale:</span>
        <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-purple-400 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-purple-600 w-full" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="libera" placeholder="">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer with reference -->
  <div class="mt-8 text-center">
    <p class="text-red-600 font-bold text-lg">Grammatica pp. <%= link_to "88", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p088"), class: "text-red-600 hover:text-red-800 underline font-bold" %>, <%= link_to "89", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p089"), class: "text-red-600 hover:text-red-800 underline font-bold" %>, <%= link_to "90", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p090"), class: "text-red-600 hover:text-red-800 underline font-bold" %>, <%= link_to "91", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p091"), class: "text-red-600 hover:text-red-800 underline font-bold" %>, <%= link_to "93", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p093"), class: "text-red-600 hover:text-red-800 underline font-bold" %></p>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise controls -->
  <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls', color: 'cyan' %>
</div>
